      en: "Presigned URLs, range streaming, HLS with adaptive bitrate (hls.js). Lyrics surface line by line in sync: a cascade with audio-based fallback, Demucs (--two-stems=vocals) + faster-whisper. Prefetch of next tracks, egress pool for third-party audio.",
    },
  },
  {
    id: "import",
    label: { ru: "Импорт", en: "Import" },
    tag: { ru: "yt-dlp · очередь", en: "yt-dlp · queue" },
    title: { ru: "Импорт из внешних источников", en: "Import from external sources" },
    desc: {
      ru: "Импорт треков, плейлистов и лайков из SoundCloud, YouTube, Bandcamp — по ссылке или каталогом. Очередь с диспетчером и лимитами (глобально / на пользователя), backfill артистов, in-app уведомления RU/EN.",
      en: "Import tracks, playlists, and likes from SoundCloud, YouTube, Bandcamp — by link or whole catalog. A queued dispatcher with global and per-user limits, artist backfill, in-app notifications in RU/EN.",
    },
  },
  {
    id: "discover",
    label: { ru: "Рекомендации", en: "Discover" },
