      en: "Elasticsearch 8: full-text over tracks and artists, search-as-you-type (SAYT), RU↔LAT transliteration, fuzzy matching. Metadata and recognized lyrics are indexed — find a track by a line from the song. Background indexing and Redis play-count drain.",
    },
